Thank you, Mr. Mayor. Yes, joining us at the press conference is Kaisa Kamm, the head of direct assistance at the Estonian Animal Protection Society. So, the joyful New Year's Eve is a bit worrisome for you. Please.
Hello also to the Estonian Animal Protection Society and first of all, I am very pleased that as the years go by, there is more and more talk about the negative impact of fireworks on both animals and the environment.
